message.entry: Only Cartesian axes support non-numeric data
Values plotted against x-axis must be {0} values. To create {1} values, use the {2} function.
At least one axis dimension is configured for {0} values. To create {1} values, use the {2} function.
Data inputs must match the axis configuration. A numeric axis must have numeric data inputs or data inputs which can be converted to double.
